Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳\N{\rE}Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳\N{\rE}Eileen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要 I-37 表格\N{\rE}I need form I-37.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 转账表格？ - 不\N{\rE}- Transfer form? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,入口 I-37.\N{\rE}Intake. I-37.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你没在听吗\N{\rE}Aren't you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她一无是处\N{\rE}She is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,弗莱博士还需要签字\N{\rE}Dr. Frye still needs to sign it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能在办公室睡觉呢\N{\rE}He's probably asleep in his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是的\N{\rE}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你可以去叫醒弗莱医生\N{\rE}Maybe you could go wake up Dr. Frye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在他耳边轻轻吹气\N{\rE}Blow softly in his ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他喜欢这样\N{\rE}He loves that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,离艾琳远点\N{\rE}Leave Eileen alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,她累了\N{\rE}She's tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是这样吗\N{\rE}Oh, is that what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为是每月都来的那事呢\N{\rE}I thought maybe it was that time of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我每个月都还来\N{\rE}At least I have a time of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你知道吗 亲爱的？\N{\rE}Oh, yeah. You know something, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不会永远都来的 你很快就会像我们一样变老\N{\rE}It won't last forever. You'll be old like us soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,纳尔逊夫人请到探视区\N{\rE}Mrs. Nelson to the visiting area, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,纳尔逊夫人请到探访区\N{\rE}Mrs. Nelson to the visiting area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会和任何人打架我告诉过你\N{\rE}I'm not gonna fight with anybody. I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,米奇怎么样了？\N{\rE}How's Mickey doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我在努力做好人\N{\rE}I'm trying to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下 坐下坐下\N{\rE}Sit down. Sit down. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 这不是我的错...\N{\rE}Well, it's not my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再见吧\N{\rE}Maybe I'll see you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我们会想念那只老狗一样\N{\rE}As much as we're gonna miss the old dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你们都能欢迎\N{\rE}I hope you'll all be welcoming
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,弗莱博士的继任者\N{\rE}to Dr. Frye's replacement on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一位优秀的年轻医生\N{\rE}A fine, fine young doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 希望孩子们能好好对待她\N{\rE}Yes, well, let's hope the boys take her seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我来对待她\N{\rE}I'll take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好好的\N{\rE}Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你好好的注射胰岛素\N{\rE}I think you will be taking your insulin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,还有退休计划吧\N{\rE}and your retirement package.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这就够了\N{\rE}That'll be enough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rE}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我会想念这里的快乐日子\N{\rE}I'll really miss all the fun around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们为弗莱博士鼓掌\N{\rE}Let's hear it for Dr. Frye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,干杯\N{\rE}Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我最近经常看到安妮\N{\rE}I see a lot of Anne these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 很多人的心都碎了\N{\rE}Yeah, a lot of broken hearts out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 亲爱的\N{\rE}Hey, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rE}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸还好吗\N{\rE}How's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rE}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 让我来\N{\rE}You know what? Let me get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rE}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,想让你进去闭上你的臭嘴\N{\rE}Want you to go inside and shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你闭嘴...你闭嘴！\N{\rE}You shut... you shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 滚开闭嘴！  - 你闭嘴\N{\rE}- Fuck off! Shut up! - You shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 该死的酒袋  - 哦 我会做...\N{\rE}- Fucking booze bag! - Oh, I'll do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要喝一杯  - 你没事吧 长官？\N{\rE}- I'm gonna have a drink. - You all right there, chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以滚蛋了\N{\rE}You can fuck right off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,问题出在隔壁该死的路德教徒身上 而不是我\N{\rE}Goddamn Lutherans next door are the problem, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人抱怨 我们只是想确保\N{\rE}Nobody's complaining. We just want to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你们会平安回家\N{\rE}you're getting home safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没人抱怨吗\N{\rE}Nobody's complaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 爸爸  - 安然无恙？\N{\rE}- Dad. - Safe and sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我为什么不能安然无恙？ - 爸爸\N{\rE}- Why wouldn't I be safe and sound? - Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我让整个街区安然无恙\N{\rE}I keep the whole fucking neighborhood safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道什么？ - 爸爸\N{\rE}- What do you know? - Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳 进去\N{\rE}E-Eileen, go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的爸爸 看我  - 进去吧\N{\rE}- Okay. Dad, look to me. - Go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧求你了 求你了\N{\rE}Come on. Please. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你惹麻烦了\N{\rE}Hey! You're causing a scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 艾琳没人想和你在一起\N{\rE}Trust me, Eileen. Nobody wants nothing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的\N{\rE}- Okay. - Mwah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 进去吧  - 姆瓦\N{\rE}- Come on. Go inside. - Mwah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的路德教徒\N{\rE}Goddamn Lutherans right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈一直很讨厌那些人\N{\rE}Your mother always hated those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 天哪 我们进去吧  - 他们可以滚了当然可以\N{\rE}- Gosh, let's go inside. - They can fuck off. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能到处去管人 爸爸\N{\rE}You can't go around policing people, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,谁说的？你知道那家伙是谁吗\N{\rE}Who says? You know who that guy was?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都在我们掌握之中 长官\N{\rE}We got it all under control, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以放轻松请吧\N{\rE}You can take it easy. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,别紧张？你他妈的别激动\N{\rE}Take it easy? Y-You fuckin' take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你不再是警察了\N{\rE}You're not a cop anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 当然\N{\rE}Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想退休 他们逼我的\N{\rE}I didn't want to retire. They made me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我太他妈擅长这个了\N{\rE}'cause I was too goddamn good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我得回局里去\N{\rE}Look, I gotta get back to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,给我倒杯酒好的\N{\rE}Pour me a drink. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,回局里去 巴克\N{\rE}Get back to the station, Buck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,把酒给我\N{\rE}Give me my drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如有需要 请给我们打电话\N{\rE}Just give us a call if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐\N{\rE}Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 过来什么味道？\N{\rE}Hey, come here. What's that smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你踩到什么东西了吗\N{\rE}Did you step in something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 怎么了？你闻到了什么？\N{\rE}No. Why? What do you smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 马路杀手\N{\rE}I don't know. Roadkill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你应该保持距离\N{\rE}Maybe you should keep your distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:09:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我会保持距离的\N{\rE}Yeah, I'll keep my distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈的在干什么？把我的鞋穿上\N{\rE}The fuck you doing? Put my fucking shoes back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但也许你应该对我好一点\N{\rE}But maybe you should be nicer to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人会忍受你的鬼话\N{\rE}No one else is gonna put up with your shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那就去吧 因为我抓到了琼妮\N{\rE}Go then, 'cause I got Joanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她可不会把房子收拾成这个样子\N{\rE}She wouldn't keep a place looking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个真正的女人 你的姐姐\N{\rE}She's a real woman, your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,而且她闻起来像个女人\N{\rE}And she smells like a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她知道如何打理家务！\N{\rE}She knows how to keep a house!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她不住在这里 而且已经结婚了！\N{\rE}And she doesn't live here, and she's married!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 因为她不是吊丝\N{\rE}Yeah, 'cause she's not a hanger-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她不想跟你说话\N{\rE}And she doesn't want to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 当然 因为她有自己的生活\N{\rE}Yeah, sure, 'cause she's made a life of her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经有所成就\N{\rE}She's made something of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,随便吧 爸爸\N{\rE}Whatever, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,过你自己的生活吧 艾琳 找点线索\N{\rE}Get a life, Eileen. Get a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\rE}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,去他妈的\N{\rE}Fuck it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 听好了\N{\rE}All right, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,众所周知 在新的一年里\N{\rE}As you know, in the new year,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将接受州审查\N{\rE}we will be up for state review.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 我们将收紧程序\N{\rE}So we're gonna be tightening our procedures
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,并根据一些重大的新想法实施新战略\N{\rE}and implementing new strategies based on some big, new ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,说到这 我左边这位新来的年轻女士\N{\rE}And on that note, this new young lady to my left,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞贝卡博士\N{\rE}Dr. Miss Rebecca St. John,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们新的监狱心理学家\N{\rE}is our new prison psychologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她刚刚完成了拉德克利夫大学的博士学位\N{\rE}She's just finished her doctorate at Radcliffe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哈佛大学\N{\rE}Harvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 哈佛\N{\rE}Ah. Harvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能不是哈佛人\N{\rE}We may not be Harvard people,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但我认为我们能跟上她\N{\rE}but I think we can keep up with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:13:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,希望她能跟上我们的步伐\N{\rE}and hopefully she can keep up with us
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们跟上了他们的步伐\N{\rE}as we keep up with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她也许很平易近人 但我向你保证\N{\rE}She may be easy on the eyes, but I assure you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她非常聪明\N{\rE}she is very smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们 我希望你们带圣约翰小姐四处转转...\N{\rE}Ladies, I hope you show Miss St. John around...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,琉璃多少钱？\N{\rE}Say, how much for a glazed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,它们是免费的\N{\rE}They're free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我开玩笑的\N{\rE}I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我是丽贝卡\N{\rE}I'm Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rE}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 这附近哪里能让女孩梳洗打扮呢？\N{\rE}Say, where can a girl get freshened up around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以演示给你看\N{\rE}I can show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 谢谢\N{\rE}Sure. Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我能拿你的外套吗\N{\rE}Can I take your jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是很可爱？谢谢\N{\rE}Aren't you sweet? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这样\N{\rE}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我没听清你的名字\N{\rE}I don't think I caught your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳\N{\rE}Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 早安  - 早上好\N{\rE}- Morning. - Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪里来？\N{\rE}Where you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:13:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？\N{\rE}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我来自纽约\N{\rE}Oh, I'm from New York originally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,曼哈顿\N{\rE}Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了剑桥 太紧张了\N{\rE}Couldn't stand Cambridge. Way too uptight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有几个人很有意思\N{\rE}Well, there were a couple of interesting people,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 不 我需要休息一下\N{\rE}but, no, I needed a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,呼吸新鲜空气\N{\rE}Get some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢海滩\N{\rE}And I love the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rE}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,32...\N{\rE}32...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,24...\N{\rE}24...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,34.\N{\rE}34.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上是我的尺寸\N{\rE}Practically my measurements.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 有些女性认为她们的身材\N{\rE}You know, some women think their figures
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,才是最重要的\N{\rE}are the only thing that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话 我觉得这有点可悲\N{\rE}Honestly, I think that's kind of pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全同意\N{\rE}I completely agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我妹妹也是这样 而且她不太聪明\N{\rE}My sister's like that, and she's not very smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很好那你和我\N{\rE}Mm, good. Then you and I
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有比我们的数字更值得讨论的事情\N{\rE}have better things to discuss than our figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管这并不是大众的观点\N{\rE}Although that isn't the popular opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你说是不是？\N{\rE}wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎流行什么\N{\rE}I don't care what's popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你\N{\rE}Well, look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一个普通的凯瑟琳·赫本\N{\rE}A regular Katharine Hepburn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如此有魄力的年轻女性实属罕见\N{\rE}Rare to meet a young woman with so much gumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是这样\N{\rE}I'm like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不管别人怎么想\N{\rE}I don't give a rat's ass what people think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可能怕你\N{\rE}They're probably scared of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,莫伊？\N{\rE}Moi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 再见\N{\rE}All right. See you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,每年\N{\rE}Every year, -
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们举行这次特别大会\N{\rE}we hold this special assembly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,庆祝主耶稣基督的诞生\N{\rE}to celebrate the birth of Our Lord Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,每年 你们中都有一个变态混蛋\N{\rE}And every year, one of you sick bastards
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,毁了我们其他人\N{\rE}ruins it for the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你最后一次不尊重圣诞节了\N{\rE}Well, you've disrespected Christmas for the last time
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,因为今年 你只能坐以待毙\N{\rE}because this year, you're gonna sit on your hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你要拉紧你的嘴唇\N{\rE}you're gonna zip your lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我看到你们有人咬人、踢人、尖叫、推人\N{\rE}If I see any of you biting, kicking, screaming, pushing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,扯头发、大笑、呻吟\N{\rE}pulling hair, laughing, moaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,或者我听到一句不中听的话\N{\rE}or I hear one wayward comment,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你们直接去洞穴\N{\rE}you're going straight to the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 话不多说\N{\rE}And now, without further ado,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我很荣幸地感谢奥利弗山的人们\N{\rE}it is my honor to thank the people from Mount Olive
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,今年再次帮助我指导盛会的人...\N{\rE}who helped me direct the pageant again this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 耶 奥利弗山  - 向你们介绍\N{\rE}- Yay, Mount Olive. - And present to you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"狱中圣诞"\N{\rE}"Christmas in Prison."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我要在圣诞节杀人\N{\rE}I'm gonna kill someone on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\rE}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我该怎么办？\N{\rE}Oh, what am I to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,被判室内禁闭三年\N{\rE}Sentenced for three years to sit indoors
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在与我信条相同的男孩中 这简直是糟糕透顶\N{\rE}among boys of my same creed, plain bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有这么多时间来策划\N{\rE}So much time to plot
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我一出来就会做什么坏事\N{\rE}what evildoings I'll undertake as soon as I get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,想吃蛋糕吗 胖子？\N{\rE}You want some cake, you fatty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,同时 我想我可以读一本书\N{\rE}In the meantime, I suppose I could read a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你不识字 混蛋\N{\rE}You can't read, motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的莎士比亚\N{\rE}Fucking Shakespeare up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在很潦倒\N{\rE}I'm scrappy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真理之书\N{\rE}Book of truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 看看麦卡利斯特\N{\rE}Oh, look at McAllister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的麦卡利斯特\N{\rE}Fucking McAllister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 架子不错！\N{\rE}Hey, nice rack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我很累了\N{\rE}Well, I'm-I'm pretty tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能在那边的谷仓里休息吗\N{\rE}Can we rest in that barn over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,总比住汽车旅馆强\N{\rE}Better than paying for a motel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你是最棒的 约瑟夫\N{\rE}You're the best, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢您带我们来这里参加人口普查\N{\rE}Thank you for taking us here to be counted in the census.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,去他妈的\N{\rE}Fuck this shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 警卫  - 等等\N{\rE}- Guard! - Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 等等 等等等等 等等  - 嘿 抓住他\N{\rE}- Wait. Wait, wait. - Hey, grab him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,后退\N{\rE}Move back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都坐下\N{\rE}All you guys sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,给我坐下\N{\rE}Sit the fuck down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 鲍勃\N{\rE}Hey, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 亲爱的\N{\rE}Hey, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这个和一包幸运糖\N{\rE}This and a pack of Luckies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真幸运 是吧？\N{\rE}Oh! It's a lucky day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 最幸运的\N{\rE}Yeah, the luckiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 香烟很不错\N{\rE}Yup. Cigarettes are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不要引火烧身\N{\rE}Don't light yourself on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你心情这么好 怎么了？\N{\rE}You're in a good mood, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 爸爸\N{\rE}Nothing's wrong, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你嘴里含着那个东西 看起来很滑稽\N{\rE}You look funny with that thing in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,今天过得怎么样 爸爸？\N{\rE}How was your day, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天过得怎么样？\N{\rE}How was my day?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rE}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一天 又是一天\N{\rE}It was a day, just another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么意义？\N{\rE}What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天过得很糟糕\N{\rE}My day was a doozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是吗\N{\rE}Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞庆典上发生了一场大战\N{\rE}A big fight broke out at the Christmas pageant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子的锁骨断了\N{\rE}Kid got his collarbone broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不为典狱长做这些文书工作\N{\rE}and I had to do all this paperwork for the warden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不要在地板上撒灰 那很俗气\N{\rE}Don't ash on the floor, it's tacky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,总之...\N{\rE}Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这是让人终生难忘的一天\N{\rE}It was one of those days you never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是吗 我永远不会忘记的日子\N{\rE}Oh, yeah? Days I'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看\N{\rE}Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,1944 年 12 月 16 日\N{\rE}December 16, 1944,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我第一次把死人的头抱在腿上\N{\rE}first time I ever held a dead man's head in my lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真是浪费\N{\rE}What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,室外气温 20 度 正在下雪\N{\rE}20 degrees outside and snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这里一样\N{\rE}Just like it is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道自己为什么会回到这个地方\N{\rE}Don't know why I ever came back to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是因为你有妻子和两个孩子\N{\rE}Maybe because you had a wife and two kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\rE}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱海滩\N{\rE}I love the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是吗 对你有好处\N{\rE}Oh, yeah? Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,战争毁了我的海滩\N{\rE}War kind of ruined beaches for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.56,0:19:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么？\N{\rE}So what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那个叫波尔克的孩子怎么样了？他说话了吗\N{\rE}How's that Polk kid? He talked yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？\N{\rE}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,波尔克\N{\rE}Polk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,刺伤父亲的孩子...\N{\rE}The kid who stabbed his father...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他或多或少是个好警察\N{\rE}who was a good cop, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,什么样的孩子会想到这样杀死自己的父亲？\N{\rE}What kind of kid thinks of killing his father like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在他睡觉时捅他一刀...\N{\rE}Stab him in his sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:19:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在他母亲面前\N{\rE}in front of his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他就坐下了\N{\rE}Then he just sits down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,从不否认\N{\rE}Never denies it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在整个审判过程中一言不发\N{\rE}Never says a word the whole trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,心理变态\N{\rE}Psychopathic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然不用担心你\N{\rE}Course I wouldn't have to worry about you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,做这样的事情 现在 我会吗\N{\rE}doing something like that, now, would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你是个女孩\N{\rE}'Cause you're a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,无法想象你拿着刀的样子\N{\rE}Can't imagine you with a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你能想象我拿着枪的样子吗\N{\rE}Can you imagine me with a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我看得出来\N{\rE}Yeah, I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天...\N{\rE}One day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,当你受够了 觉得...\N{\rE}when you've had enough and you feel like, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,躲开\N{\rE}ducking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,也许等我死后\N{\rE}Maybe when I'm dead and gone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你谁也没有 永远也不会有\N{\rE}and you got nobody and you never will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我能想象得到\N{\rE}I could imagine that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不会 对吧？\N{\rE}But you wouldn't, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你太厉害了\N{\rE}'Cause you're too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,说 给我一支烟\N{\rE}Say, give me one of those cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么 老金？\N{\rE}What have you got, Old Gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rE}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢老金\N{\rE}I like Old Gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rE}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.98,0:22:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀\N{\rE}Oopsie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,需要帮助吗\N{\rE}Do you need any help?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我没事\N{\rE}Uh, no, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.75,0:22:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就是黄油手指\N{\rE}Just butterfingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该看看我\N{\rE}You should see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.39,0:22:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我笨手笨脚的\N{\rE}I'm a total klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.73,0:22:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 对了\N{\rE}Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.17,0:22:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,李·波尔克\N{\rE}Lee Polk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.23,0:22:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不是每天都能看到的\N{\rE}That's not something you see every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 很糟糕\N{\rE}Yeah, it's pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.24,0:22:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,睡前阅读？\N{\rE}Bedtime reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在整理文件\N{\rE}I was just doing some filing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天的表演真精彩\N{\rE}That's some show yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.02,0:22:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他们每年都这样做\N{\rE}They do it every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.49,0:22:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这是残忍和不寻常的惩罚\N{\rE}I'd call that cruel and unusual punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起我通常不抽烟\N{\rE}Sorry. I don't usually smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个令人讨厌的习惯\N{\rE}It's a nasty habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我喜欢它的原因\N{\rE}That's why I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.17,0:23:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 这可不像一位淑女\N{\rE}Not very becoming of a lady, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,使牙齿变黄\N{\rE}Turns your teeth yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.91,0:23:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吗\N{\rE}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是香烟和咖啡\N{\rE}That's cigarettes and coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.75,0:23:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,还有红酒\N{\rE}And red wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.15,0:23:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你的牙齿很完美\N{\rE}No, your teeth are perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.52,0:23:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喝咖啡\N{\rE}I don't drink coffee,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.16,0:23:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我的牙齿应该没问题 但是...\N{\rE}so my teeth should be fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,都烂了\N{\rE}they're all rotted
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我特别爱吃甜食\N{\rE}due to my extreme propensity for sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢甜食\N{\rE}A propensity for sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.83,0:23:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你的生活还不够甜蜜吗\N{\rE}You don't get enough sweetness in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是吃了很多糖果\N{\rE}I just eat a lot of candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 看着你我都不知道\N{\rE}Mm. I wouldn't know it to look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你真娇小\N{\rE}You're so petite.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.47,0:23:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 个子高也有个子高的好处\N{\rE}Being tall has its advantages, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.34,0:23:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但对我来说 大多数男人都太矮了\N{\rE}but most men are just too short for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.88,0:23:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你注意到了吗 还是我在胡思乱想？\N{\rE}Have you noticed, or am I imagining things,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:23:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的男人越来越矮\N{\rE}that men these days are getting shorter and shorter,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.59,0:24:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,更秃 更胖？\N{\rE}balder, and fatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.89,0:24:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这里所有的男人都是小男孩\N{\rE}All the men around here are little boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.53,0:24:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你真有趣\N{\rE}You're funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.73,0:24:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说在监狱外面\N{\rE}I meant outside this prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然你说得对\N{\rE}Although you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.83,0:24:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,守卫 典狱长\N{\rE}The guards, the warden,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.10,0:24:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,它们没什么好看的\N{\rE}they're not much to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.77,0:24:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该去看弗莱医生的\N{\rE}You should have seen Dr. Frye.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.84,0:24:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他长得真的很猥琐\N{\rE}He was really pretty nasty looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.64,0:24:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我对此并不感到惊讶\N{\rE}That doesn't surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.24,0:24:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我的办公室并不宽敞\N{\rE}My office isn't very becoming,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.64,0:24:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而这一切都散发着肮脏皮革的味道\N{\rE}and it all smells of dirty leather.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.31,0:24:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始怀疑里面到底发生了什么\N{\rE}I'm beginning to wonder what went on in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.31,0:24:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么好东西\N{\rE}Nothing good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.28,0:24:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 我从未真正进过那间办公室\N{\rE}I mean, I never actually been in that office.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.19,0:24:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你有空应该过来看看\N{\rE}Oh. Well, you should come by sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.02,0:24:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然门是关着的\N{\rE}Although if the door's closed,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.16,0:24:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这意味着我和其中一个男孩在一起\N{\rE}that means I'm with one of the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.59,0:24:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rE}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.90,0:24:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道不害怕吗\N{\rE}Aren't you ever scared
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.53,0:24:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人和他们在一起？\N{\rE}being alone in there with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.73,0:24:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rE}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.57,0:24:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有空来找我 好吗\N{\rE}Come by, and see me sometime, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.40,0:24:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 如果你听到我在里面尖叫的话\N{\rE}Although, you know, if you hear me screaming in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.21,0:24:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,请随时踢门救我\N{\rE}feel free to kick down the door and rescue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.27,0:24:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rE}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.51,0:24:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我开玩笑的 亲爱的\N{\rE}I'm just kidding, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.64,0:24:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有蜂鸣器\N{\rE}There's a buzzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.13,0:25:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来见伦纳德·波尔克的\N{\rE}I'm here to see Leonard Polk.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.54,0:25:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮·波尔克\N{\rE}Anne Polk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.31,0:26:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你不在日程表上\N{\rE}You're not on the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.91,0:26:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你是后来加入的吗\N{\rE}Are you a late addition?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.85,0:26:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我是被叫来的\N{\rE}I-I was called.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.25,0:26:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 我现在就在这里\N{\rE}I don't know, I-I'm here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.36,0:26:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要填写一份表格\N{\rE}Well, you need to fill out a form.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.23,0:26:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是邓洛普酋长的孩子吗\N{\rE}Aren't you Chief Dunlop's kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.83,0:26:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rE}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.06,0:26:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也是\N{\rE}I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.07,0:26:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,波尔克夫人？我是圣约翰医生\N{\rE}Mrs. Polk? I'm Dr. St. John.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.67,0:26:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们通过电话 非常感谢你能来\N{\rE}We spoke on the phone. Thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.97,0:26:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 没必要这么麻烦\N{\rE}Oh, no need to bother with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.07,0:26:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道你是谁\N{\rE}We all know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.41,0:26:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳 你能帮我们开门吗\N{\rE}Eileen, would you help us with the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.58,0:26:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rE}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.88,0:26:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样的\N{\rE}It's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.65,0:26:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,拿上你的外套？\N{\rE}Take your coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.95,0:26:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,请\N{\rE}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.42,0:26:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 艾琳\N{\rE}Thank you, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.60,0:26:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你先请\N{\rE}After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.01,0:27:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要这样对我？\N{\rE}Why are you doing this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.47,0:27:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？\N{\rE}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.37,0:27:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你有话要说吗\N{\rE}You got something to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.75,0:27:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,让我出去\N{\rE}Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.95,0:27:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,让我出去让我出去\N{\rE}Let me out! Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.15,0:27:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,让我出去\N{\rE}Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.29,0:27:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你们...你们想怎么处置他就怎么处置他\N{\rE}Y-You do... y'all do what you want with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.06,0:28:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至不愿意和自己的母亲说话？\N{\rE}Won't even talk to his own mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.23,0:28:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直是个讨厌的孩子\N{\rE}He's always been a nasty boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.23,0:28:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,一个肮脏下流的男孩\N{\rE}A filthy, nasty boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.07,0:28:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要锁门\N{\rE}I need to lock up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.67,0:28:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上 探视时间在 20 分钟前就已经结束了\N{\rE}Visitation hours were actually over 20 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.87,0:28:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我明白了\N{\rE}Oh, I-I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.74,0:28:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你想在我的办公室里继续说话吗\N{\rE}Would you like to keep talking in my office?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.35,0:28:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们走  - 转过去\N{\rE}- Let's go. - Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.28,0:28:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不用了没这个必要\N{\rE}Oh, no. That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.52,0:28:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我得把他铐起来  - 不\N{\rE}- I need to cuff him. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.26,0:28:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 李没事的\N{\rE}Don't worry, Lee. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.27,0:28:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没有这个必要\N{\rE}That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.07,0:28:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样她是个医生\N{\rE}Don't do that. She's a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.04,0:28:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得她需要看医生\N{\rE}I think she needs a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.24,0:28:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子杀了个警察\N{\rE}That kid killed a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.28,0:28:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他杀死了自己的父亲\N{\rE}He killed his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.24,0:28:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这两者是有区别的\N{\rE}There's a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.48,0:28:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 真对不起让我看看是谁\N{\rE}Oh, I'm so sorry. Let me see who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.45,0:29:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 艾琳\N{\rE}Oh, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.25,0:29:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么能帮您的吗\N{\rE}Um, can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.83,0:29:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘带笔记本了\N{\rE}You forgot your notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.33,0:29:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 太谢谢你了\N{\rE}Oh, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.06,0:29:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的需要这个\N{\rE}I actually need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.30,0:29:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 希望你没读过\N{\rE}Um, hope you didn't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.23,0:29:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 当然不是  - 当然没有\N{\rE}- No, of course not. - Oh, no,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.67,0:29:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我开玩笑的 只是鸡爪而已\N{\rE}I'm just kidding. It's just chicken scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.74,0:29:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 艾琳\N{\rE}Wait. Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.24,0:29:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不是想咄咄逼人\N{\rE}I don't mean to be forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.71,0:29:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 嗯 你可能已经有其他计划了\N{\rE}and, um, you probably have other plans already,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.85,0:29:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 今晚我能请你喝一杯吗\N{\rE}but, um, can I take you to a drink tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.25,0:29:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这个该死的镇子里一个人都不认识\N{\rE}I don't know anyone in this darn town,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.85,0:29:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意 我很乐意请你喝鸡尾酒\N{\rE}and I'd love to treat you to a cocktail if you're game.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.09,0:29:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的\N{\rE}- Okay. - Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.62,0:29:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我拧了你的胳膊？\N{\rE}I've twisted your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.16,0:29:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 谁调制的马提尼最好喝？\N{\rE}So, uh, who makes the best martini in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.43,0:29:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也许是奥哈拉餐厅？\N{\rE}- Maybe O'Hara's? - O'Hara's.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.36,0:29:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上 这是镇上唯一的一家酒吧\N{\rE}It's actually the only bar in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.90,0:29:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不 奥哈拉餐厅很不错\N{\rE}No, O'Hara's is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.10,0:29:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,7 点见？\N{\rE}See you at 7:00?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.47,0:29:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,带着铃铛？是这个意思吗\N{\rE}With bells on? Is that the expression?
