Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.24,0:31:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,5)\an9\fs12\i1}♪你会是真实的\N{\rL}{\i1\fs9}♪ That you'll be true ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.25,0:31:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,5)\an9\fs12\i1}♪因为毫无疑问...\N{\rL}{\i1\fs9}♪ For there is no doubt... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.89,0:31:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 艾琳\N{\rE}- Hi. - Oh, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.09,0:31:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rE}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.46,0:31:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐下\N{\rE}Please, please, please, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.83,0:31:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你要吃什么？\N{\rE}Um, what are you having?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.53,0:31:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 我想我还是喝啤酒吧\N{\rE}Uh, I'll have a beer, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.10,0:31:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啤酒？哦\N{\rE}A beer? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.73,0:32:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 艾琳\N{\rE}Hi, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.97,0:32:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你 亲爱的\N{\rE}Good to see you, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.07,0:32:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来呢 亲爱的？\N{\rE}What's next, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.17,0:32:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...我的天啊\N{\rE}Um, well... Oh, my stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.51,0:32:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你绝对冻僵了\N{\rE}You're absolutely frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.08,0:32:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,请给我一杯啤酒 也许再来点威士忌\N{\rE}Um, one beer, please, and maybe a little whiskey
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.51,0:32:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,来温暖我的女孩怎么样？\N{\rE}to warm up my girl. What say, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.45,0:32:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 你看起来真迷人\N{\rE}My, you look very glamorous.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.65,0:32:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是一件旧衣服\N{\rE}It's just an old dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.99,0:32:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗\N{\rE}May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.83,0:32:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢 亲爱的？再来杯马提尼？\N{\rE}How about you, sweetheart? Another martini?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.90,0:32:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,爱一个谢谢\N{\rE}Love one. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.26,0:32:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这次我们先不要吃橄榄\N{\rE}Maybe let's hold the olives this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.70,0:32:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我很难找到这个地方\N{\rE}I thought I'd have a hard time finding this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.67,0:32:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但还是来了\N{\rE}but here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.91,0:32:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\rE}You feeling all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.01,0:32:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\rE}Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.68,0:32:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我的车有点问题\N{\rE}Uh, there's something wrong with my car,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.45,0:32:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我必须关着车窗开车\N{\rE}so I have to drive with the windows down,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.39,0:32:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,否则就会烟雾弥漫\N{\rE}or else it fills with smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.25,0:32:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你在开玩笑\N{\rE}Oh, you're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.52,0:32:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这听起来太可怕了\N{\rE}That sounds absolutely awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.12,0:32:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不能让你丈夫帮你修好吗\N{\rE}Can't you get your husband to fix that for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.23,0:33:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不 我还没结婚\N{\rE}Oh, no, I'm not married.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.33,0:33:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都是单身\N{\rE}I've always been single.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.23,0:33:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,当我身边有男人的时候\N{\rE}And when I do have a guy around,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.73,0:33:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,只是为了好玩 而且时间很短\N{\rE}it's just for fun, and it's brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.77,0:33:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我从不在任何地方久留\N{\rE}No, I never stay anywhere long with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.24,0:33:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我的生活方式\N{\rE}Sort of my modus vivendi
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.21,0:33:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,或我的病态 这取决于我在跟谁说话\N{\rE}or my pathology, depending on who I'm talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.68,0:33:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,您在摩尔黑德工作多久了？\N{\rE}How long have you worked at Moorehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.28,0:33:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,三四年\N{\rE}Three or four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.28,0:33:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 本来只是暂时的\N{\rE}Uh, it was only supposed to be temporary,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.69,0:33:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲生病期间 我搬回来住了一段时间\N{\rE}while I moved back for a bit while my mother was sick,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.06,0:33:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然后她死了 所以\N{\rE}and then she died, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.39,0:33:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在监狱里 时间过得飞快\N{\rE}I've been at the prison, and time's just flown by.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.33,0:33:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 上帝啊\N{\rE}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.70,0:33:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,监狱不是时光飞逝的地方\N{\rE}Prison is no place for time to fly by.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.10,0:33:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你母亲的死\N{\rE}And your mother dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.04,0:33:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,对一位年轻女士来说 这已经够多了\N{\rE}That's a lot for a young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.11,0:33:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 24.\N{\rE}Ah. 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.61,0:33:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那你一定很想再出去走走 是吗\N{\rE}Then you must be eager to get back out there. Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.35,0:33:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 嗯 我也是个孤儿\N{\rE}You know, um, I'm an orphan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.75,0:34:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我叔叔在西部把我抚养长大\N{\rE}My uncle raised me out West.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.59,0:34:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,阳光普照的地方\N{\rE}Where the sun shines.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.13,0:34:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白你们是怎么做到的\N{\rE}I don't understand how you all do it here,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.63,0:34:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一个冬天又一个冬天\N{\rE}winter after winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.63,0:34:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真让人毛骨悚然我也不知道\N{\rE}It's positively creepy. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.03,0:34:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我对新英格兰有着一种奇怪的情结\N{\rE}I'm in a sort of strange love affair with New England.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.43,0:34:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢它 但也讨厌它\N{\rE}I love it, but I also hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.44,0:34:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的一切都很真实 不是吗\N{\rE}Things feel very real here, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.51,0:34:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,算是没有...\N{\rE}Sort of there's no...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.98,0:34:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,想象力\N{\rE}imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.28,0:34:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没有感伤 也没有幻想\N{\rE}There's no sentimentality or fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.81,0:34:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这里...这里无处可藏\N{\rE}There's... there's just nowhere to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.45,0:34:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\rE}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.36,0:34:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝多了\N{\rE}I've had too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.09,0:34:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我一喝多就爱说话\N{\rE}I tend to talk when I've had too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.46,0:34:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\rE}It's all right.
