Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.50,0:34:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,她跟你说什么了吗\N{\rE}Did she say anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.07,0:34:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,波尔克夫人？\N{\rE}Mrs. Polk?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.71,0:34:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她只是心烦意乱\N{\rE}She was just upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.21,0:34:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那些母亲总是不高兴\N{\rE}Those mothers are always upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.78,0:35:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rE}Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.82,0:35:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得她是个愤怒的女人吗\N{\rE}Did she seem like an angry woman to you?
