Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.23,0:43:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,差点撞车\N{\rE}Nearly crashed the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.80,0:43:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,睡在自己的病床上\N{\rE}Sleeping in your own sick,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.80,0:43:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你又在担心能否准时上班？\N{\rE}and now you're worried about getting to work on time?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.10,0:43:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我几乎不敢看你 我太惭愧了\N{\rE}I can hardly look at you, I'm so ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.27,0:43:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,奥利弗·忒斯特会对这个家感激不尽\N{\rE}Oliver Twist would be grateful for this home,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.84,0:43:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你 艾琳\N{\rE}but you, Eileen,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.54,0:43:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你是垃圾 艾琳 就是垃圾\N{\rE}you're trash, Eileen, just trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.18,0:43:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我所做的就是和一个女同事约会\N{\rE}All I did was go out with a girl from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.51,0:43:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你和一个女同事约会了？\N{\rE}You went out with a girl from work?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.05,0:43:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我看起来像昨天才出生的吗\N{\rE}Do I look like I was born yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.55,0:43:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他是谁？他是谁？\N{\rE}Who is he? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.12,0:43:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这个男孩是谁？我只想知道他是谁\N{\rE}Who is this boy? I just want to know who he is
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.29,0:44:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在你怀孕并把灵魂出卖给撒旦之前\N{\rE}before you get knocked up and sell your soul to Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.22,0:44:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你能把钥匙给我吗\N{\rE}Can you just give me the keys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.79,0:44:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了我要迟到了\N{\rE}Please! I'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.33,0:44:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你穿成这样哪儿也去不了\N{\rE}You're not going anywhere dressed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.39,0:44:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 真的 艾琳 你怎么敢？\N{\rE}I mean, really, Eileen, how dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.70,0:44:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你母亲在我父亲葬礼上穿的衣服\N{\rE}That's the dress your mother wore to my father's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.73,0:44:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你不尊重任何人\N{\rE}You got no respect for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.90,0:44:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,换衣服\N{\rE}Get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.34,0:44:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让任何人看到你穿成这样\N{\rE}I don't want anyone seeing you in that getup.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.84,0:44:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会以为我死了\N{\rE}They'll think I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.65,0:44:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,邓洛普小姐？邓洛普小姐？\N{\rE}Ah. Miss Dunlop?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.45,0:44:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我能说句话吗\N{\rE}May I, um, may I have a word?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.85,0:44:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\rE}Oh, Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.12,0:44:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是关于你父亲的\N{\rE}It's about your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.52,0:44:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他？去和他谈谈他在里面\N{\rE}Him? Go talk to him. He's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.89,0:44:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是关于他的枪\N{\rE}It's about his gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.16,0:44:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这应该不错\N{\rE}This oughta be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.56,0:44:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,请告诉我 巴克\N{\rE}Pray tell, Buck.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.69,0:44:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 昨天\N{\rE}Uh, yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.06,0:44:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们收到了几位邻居的投诉\N{\rE}we got several complaints from neighbors,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.03,0:44:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,学校的康妮小姐寄来的\N{\rE}from Miss Connie down at the school,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.77,0:44:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,邓洛普局长\N{\rE}that, uh, Chief Dunlop
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.74,0:44:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在朝北的窗前\N{\rE}was sitting in that north-facing window
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.44,0:44:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,并用武器指着他\N{\rE}and, uh, pointing his weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.11,0:44:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们放学回家的路上\N{\rE}at children walking home from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.34,0:44:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他已同意将财产交由您照管\N{\rE}He has agreed to relinquish the property into your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.75,0:45:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你保证不把它用在他身上\N{\rE}As long as you promise not to use it on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.22,0:45:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他的话\N{\rE}His words.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.69,0:45:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以进来吗\N{\rE}May I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.15,0:45:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,想把它像装饰品一样挂在我身上吗\N{\rE}Want to hang it on me like an ornament?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.06,0:45:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,胡\N{\rE}Aw.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.26,0:45:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信邓洛普小姐\N{\rE}I'm sure that Miss Dunlop
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.16,0:45:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,会好好保管武器的 长官\N{\rE}will take excellent care of the weapon, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.26,0:45:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,正如她对所有事情的态度一样 巴克 你也看到了\N{\rE}As she does with all things, Buck, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.61,0:45:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,5)\an9\fs12\i1}♪圣诞时节\N{\rL}{\i1\fs9}♪ It's Christmastime ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.45,0:45:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,5)\an9\fs12\i1}♪我想见圣诞老人\N{\rL}{\i1\fs9}♪ And I wanna see Santa Claus ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.89,0:45:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,5)\an9\fs12\i1}♪什么？什么？\N{\rL}{\i1\fs9}♪ What? What? What? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.09,0:45:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,5)\an9\fs12\i1}♪是的 这是圣诞节\N{\rL}{\i1\fs9}♪ Yes, it's Christmastime ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.32,0:45:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,5)\an9\fs12\i1}♪我想见圣诞老人\N{\rL}{\i1\fs9}♪ And I wanna see Santa Claus ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.73,0:45:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,5)\an9\fs12\i1}♪什么？什么？\N{\rL}{\i1\fs9}♪ What? What? What? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.23,0:45:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,5)\an9\fs12\i1}♪会问他我的宝贝\N{\rL}{\i1\fs9}♪ Gonna ask him for my baby ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.50,0:45:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,5)\an9\fs12\i1}♪这不是一个真正的好理由？\N{\rL}{\i1\fs9}♪ Ain't that a real good cause? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.20,0:45:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,让我知道是哪些\N{\rE}Let me know which ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.54,0:45:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 我等着\N{\rE}Sure. I'll hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.84,0:45:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 看那只猫叼来了什么？\N{\rE}Ah, look what the cat dragged in.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.57,0:46:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,下午好 艾琳\N{\rE}Good afternoon, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.11,0:46:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来像雏菊一样鲜艳 一如既往\N{\rE}You look fresh as a daisy, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.21,0:46:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我的车出了问题\N{\rE}I had car trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.45,0:46:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我相信麻烦的部分\N{\rE}Yeah, I believe the trouble part.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.88,0:46:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,快到圣诞节了 你能让我休息一下吗\N{\rE}It's almost Christmas. Can you give me a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.25,0:46:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不 去工作\N{\rE}No. Get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.22,0:46:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 我需要波尔克的文件\N{\rE}Okay. I need the Polk file.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.49,0:46:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rE}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.12,0:46:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我想是圣约翰博士干的\N{\rE}I think Dr. St. John has it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.16,0:46:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好极了是的 恐怕那个\N{\rE}Perfect. Yeah, I'm afraid that one
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.53,0:46:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,只能等到假期结束后了\N{\rE}will have to wait till after the holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.56,0:46:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们新来了一位医生\N{\rE}We have a new doctor on staff,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.33,0:46:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,显然她不遵守程序\N{\rE}and, uh, apparently she doesn't follow procedures.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.70,0:46:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她今天没来？ - 已经走了\N{\rE}- She's not in today? - Been and gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.70,0:46:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她圣诞节后就会回来\N{\rE}She's gonna be back after Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.10,0:46:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好的好的\N{\rE}Yeah. Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.17,0:46:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧谢谢\N{\rE}All right, then. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.84,0:46:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\rE}Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.21,0:46:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你想去哪儿？\N{\rE}Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.28,0:46:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,医务室\N{\rE}The infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.65,0:46:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得周围有什么东西在流动\N{\rE}I think something's going around.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.38,0:46:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来好像到处跑\N{\rE}You look like you've been going around.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.19,0:46:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个酒鬼\N{\rE}She's a boozer.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.66,0:49:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸？\N{\rE}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.11,0:49:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸？\N{\rE}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.25,0:50:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸？\N{\rE}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.69,0:50:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 你能听到我吗\N{\rE}Dad, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.06,0:50:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 你能听到我吗\N{\rE}Dad, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.56,0:50:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在上面干什么？ - 我需要我的枪\N{\rE}- What were you doing up there? - I need my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.36,0:50:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 坐起来  - 它在追我\N{\rE}- Sit up. - It's after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.43,0:50:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没人追杀你\N{\rE}Nobody's after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.43,0:50:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,坐起来坐起来\N{\rE}Sit up. Sit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.27,0:50:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,琼妮\N{\rE}Joanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.97,0:50:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是你吗 琼妮？\N{\rE}That you, Joanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.98,0:50:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rE}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.01,0:50:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,琼妮琼妮\N{\rE}Joanie. Joanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.72,0:50:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,琼妮\N{\rE}Joanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.22,0:50:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\rE}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.75,0:50:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,别大惊小怪的 琼妮\N{\rE}Quit your fussing, Joanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.07,0:50:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们给他缝合了伤口\N{\rE}We stitched him up,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.47,0:50:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为他有脑震荡\N{\rE}and I don't think he has a concussion,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.14,0:50:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但他血液中的酒精含量\N{\rE}but his blood alcohol level
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.54,0:50:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是 1·7 点\N{\rE}is point one-seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.11,0:51:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他的肝脏肿大 浑身是伤\N{\rE}His liver's enlarged, and he's covered in bruises.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.34,0:51:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是责怪你 亲爱的 但是...\N{\rE}I'm not blaming you, honey, but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.88,0:51:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 当然\N{\rE}Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.04,0:51:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 是谁让他这样生活的？\N{\rE}Hey, who's letting him live like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.85,0:51:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我妈妈去世了 他也没有工作\N{\rE}I don't know. My mom died, and he doesn't have a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.25,0:51:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他还能做什么？\N{\rE}What else is he supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.78,0:51:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 有些男人不会整天喝酒\N{\rE}Yeah, there are men who don't drink all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.48,0:51:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rE}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.15,0:51:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我知道这对你来说很难 但是...\N{\rE}Look, I know this is hard for you, but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.92,0:51:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他不喝酒 他可能会死\N{\rE}if he stops drinking, he might die,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.19,0:51:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果他继续酗酒 肯定会要了他的命\N{\rE}but if he keeps drinking, it'll definitely kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.00,0:51:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道还能对你说什么\N{\rE}I don't know what else to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.07,0:51:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下 爸爸\N{\rE}Sit down, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.41,0:51:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,医生说你快死了\N{\rE}The doctor told me you're gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.52,0:51:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 好像他没有？\N{\rE}Oh, like he's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.49,0:51:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他说 如果你继续这样喝下去\N{\rE}He said, if you keep drinking like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.36,0:51:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,它会杀了你\N{\rE}it'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.56,0:51:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,去他的\N{\rE}Screw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.13,0:51:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他们在那家医院杀了你母亲\N{\rE}You know they killed your mother at that hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.63,0:51:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他们欠我的不只是缝针\N{\rE}They owe me more than stitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.06,0:51:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你能往后靠吗\N{\rE}Can you lean back?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.10,0:51:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然可以往后靠\N{\rE}Course I can lean back.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.43,0:52:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我不知道怎么上床睡觉吗\N{\rE}You don't think I know how to go to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.60,0:52:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我要喝一杯\N{\rE}Well, I need a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.81,0:52:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\rE}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.87,0:52:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 我不在这里睡觉\N{\rE}And anyway, I do not sleep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.57,0:52:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 闹鬼了  - 求你了 爸爸\N{\rE}- It's haunted. - Please, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.44,0:52:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我给你拿个瓶子 你会躺下吗\N{\rE}If I get you a bottle, will you lie down?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.61,0:52:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我想和我女儿喝一杯\N{\rE}No. I want to have a drink with my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.68,0:52:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在不一样了\N{\rE}You're different these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.68,0:52:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你几乎很有趣\N{\rE}You're almost interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.99,0:52:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你用工作赚来的钱做了什么？\N{\rE}What are you doing with all the money you make at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.00,0:52:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不买自己的衣服？\N{\rE}Why don't you ever buy your own clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.31,0:52:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得那件大衣\N{\rE}I remember that coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.51,0:52:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得你的母亲...\N{\rE}I remember your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.32,0:52:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我穿起来怎么样？\N{\rE}How does it look on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.02,0:52:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈穿那件大衣真漂亮\N{\rE}Well, your mother looked beautiful in that coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.29,0:52:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我买给她穿的\N{\rE}I bought it for her to wear
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.99,0:52:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,当她走出船舱时\N{\rE}when she got out of the bughouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.76,0:53:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直很爱你的母亲\N{\rE}I always loved your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.16,0:53:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你觉得它看起来像什么\N{\rE}No matter what you thought it looked like,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.80,0:53:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直很爱她\N{\rE}I always loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.97,0:53:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道人们是怎么说我的\N{\rE}And I know what people say about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.24,0:53:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说是我把她逼疯的 因为我是个硬骨头\N{\rE}They say I made her crazy 'cause I'm a hard-ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.08,0:53:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能还大喊了几声\N{\rE}And I may have yelled a few times,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.18,0:53:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但她总是原谅我\N{\rE}but she always forgave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.19,0:53:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们彼此相爱\N{\rE}Because we loved each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.69,0:53:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,爱会让你疯狂 艾琳\N{\rE}Love will make you crazy, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.96,0:53:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能永远都不会明白\N{\rE}You'll probably never understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.79,0:53:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\rE}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.70,0:53:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人...\N{\rE}Some people...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.83,0:53:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们才是真正的人\N{\rE}they're the real people.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.14,0:53:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就像电影一样 你看的就是他们\N{\rE}Like in a movie, they're the ones you're watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.47,0:53:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是他们在行动\N{\rE}They're the ones making moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.21,0:53:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,而其他人...\N{\rE}And the other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.15,0:53:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,它们只是在那里填充空间\N{\rE}they're just there filling the space,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.95,0:54:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而你却认为这是理所当然的\N{\rE}and you take 'em for granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.45,0:54:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得 "他们很容易"\N{\rE}You think, "They're easy."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.42,0:54:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,拿一分钱 留一分钱\N{\rE}Take a penny, leave a penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.73,0:54:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你 艾琳\N{\rE}That's you, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.63,0:54:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是其中之一\N{\rE}You're one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.19,0:54:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么？你不用锁门\N{\rE}What are you doing? You don't gotta lock it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.46,0:54:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\N{\rE}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.03,0:54:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 来吧\N{\rE}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.53,0:54:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧外面很冷\N{\rE}Come on. It's cold out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.34,0:54:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快点快点\N{\rE}Come on. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.34,0:54:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,开门\N{\rE}Open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.04,0:54:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真他妈重\N{\rE}Fucking heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.25,0:55:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,把他妈的酒给我\N{\rE}Give me my fucking drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.68,0:55:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳\N{\rE}Eileen!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.72,0:55:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳\N{\rE}Eileen!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.19,0:55:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 爸爸？\N{\rE}What, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.62,0:55:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,电话响了\N{\rE}Phone rang.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.09,0:55:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有个女人在找你\N{\rE}Some woman looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.73,0:55:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么？\N{\rE}What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.13,0:55:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有\N{\rE}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.06,0:55:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都不知道 我什么也没说\N{\rE}I know nothing. I said nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.34,0:55:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rE}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.54,0:56:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 圣诞天使\N{\rE}Hello, Christmas angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.41,0:56:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,丽贝卡？\N{\rE}Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.11,0:56:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我只是在想你\N{\rE}Look, I was just thinking of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.68,0:56:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rE}and, well, I-I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.05,0:56:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,平安夜有什么计划\N{\rE}what you're planning for Christmas Eve,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.45,0:56:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想也许你愿意过来\N{\rE}but I thought maybe you'd like to come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.39,0:56:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以播放一些唱片\N{\rE}There are some records we could play,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.95,0:56:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果一切顺利 也许还能再跳一次舞\N{\rE}and maybe dance again if all goes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.99,0:56:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 除非你有更好的提议\N{\rE}Unless you have a better offer, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.79,0:56:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有更好的提议\N{\rE}I don't have a better offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.06,0:56:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那你会来吗  - 好啊\N{\rE}- So you'll come? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.86,0:56:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,让我把地址告诉你\N{\rE}Let me give you the address.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.80,0:56:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 等一下\N{\rE}Okay. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.27,0:56:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,枫树街 32 号\N{\rE}It's 32 Maple Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.67,0:56:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\rE}So see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.64,0:56:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再见  - 再见\N{\rE}- Bye. - Bye.
