Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.85,0:57:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,5)\an9\fs12\i1}♪太快了\N{\rL}{\i1\fs9}♪ All too soon ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.62,0:57:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,5)\an9\fs12\i1}♪我的秘密爱情\N{\rL}{\i1\fs9}♪ My secret love ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.06,0:57:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,5)\an9\fs12\i1}♪成为...\N{\rL}{\i1\fs9}♪ Became... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.93,0:58:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哦！\N{\rE}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.33,0:58:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你来了\N{\rE}Y-You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.30,0:58:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个圣诞奇迹\N{\rE}It's a Christmas miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.77,0:58:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我花了这么长时间\N{\rE}Sorry it took me so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.64,0:58:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得那只猫中邪了\N{\rE}I think that cat's possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.51,0:58:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐\N{\rE}Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.61,0:58:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哦你不是桃子吗\N{\rE}Oh. Aren't you a peach?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.98,0:58:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧\N{\rE}Come in! Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.91,0:58:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳\N{\rE}Eileen, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.25,0:58:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉这里一团糟\N{\rE}I'm sorry the place is such a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.05,0:58:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有...我是说 我试着清理了一下\N{\rE}I-I haven't... I mean, I tried to clean it up a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.32,0:58:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但我实在想不通\N{\rE}but it's just beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.92,0:58:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望这不会让你感到不舒服\N{\rE}I hope it doesn't make you uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.06,0:58:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们打开这瓶酒\N{\rE}Let's open this wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.09,0:58:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 坐下 坐下 坐下\N{\rE}Uh, sit down. Sit down. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.49,0:58:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,5)\an9\fs12\i1}♪你是多么美好...\N{\rL}{\i1\fs9}♪ Just how wonderful you are... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.43,0:58:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你不用开很远 远吗\N{\rE}I hope you didn't have to drive far. Was it far?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.97,0:58:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没有我开车到处跑\N{\rE}Uh, no. I drive all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.97,0:58:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你拿外套\N{\rE}Let me take your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.37,0:58:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢  - 哦 天哪\N{\rE}- Thanks. - Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.51,0:58:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,它又漂亮又柔软\N{\rE}It's so nice and soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.88,0:58:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我妈妈的\N{\rE}It's my mother's.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.41,0:58:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,她一定是个非常优雅的女士\N{\rE}Well, uh, she must have been a real classy lady
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.65,0:58:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个如此优雅的女儿\N{\rE}to have such a classy daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.65,0:58:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 她是个衣架子\N{\rE}She was something of a clotheshorse, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.39,0:59:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,希望是你喜欢的那种\N{\rE}I hope it's a kind you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.09,0:59:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 一定很好吃\N{\rE}Oh. I'm sure it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.89,0:59:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,其实 喝酒听起来不错\N{\rE}Drink sounds nice, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.59,0:59:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们看看开瓶器藏在哪里\N{\rE}Let's see where the corkscrew's hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.39,0:59:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 你知道\N{\rE}Uh, you know, -
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.33,0:59:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我最近太忙了\N{\rE}I have just been so busy lately
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.23,0:59:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我似乎记不起在哪里...\N{\rE}that I can't seem to remember where the...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.57,0:59:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但它一定就在这些乱七八糟的东西下面 对吗\N{\rE}But it's got to be here under all this mess, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.60,0:59:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\rE}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.27,0:59:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一位心灵手巧的年轻博士生曾经教过我一招\N{\rE}A very handy young PhD student once taught me a trick
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.24,0:59:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果您遇到困难 如何打开瓶子？\N{\rE}for how to open a bottle if you're ever stranded
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.74,0:59:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没有开瓶器\N{\rE}without a corkscrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.72,0:59:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哲学家总是最大的酒鬼\N{\rE}Philosophers are always the biggest drunks.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.72,0:59:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然他有点可爱\N{\rE}Although he was kind of cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.00,0:59:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,尤金·亨德森 哈佛大学\N{\rE}Eugene Henderson, Harvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.47,0:59:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你还能这么做\N{\rE}I had no idea you could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.77,0:59:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这一招真不错\N{\rE}That was a great trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.24,0:59:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rE}Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.97,0:59:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们需要一些眼镜\N{\rE}Now we need some glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.61,0:59:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\rE}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.14,0:59:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳 我的圣诞救星\N{\rE}So to Eileen, my Christmas savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.78,0:59:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,救世主？\N{\rE}Savior?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.15,1:00:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都没做\N{\rE}I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.58,1:00:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你是个朋友\N{\rE}Well, you're being a friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.05,1:00:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是一切 干杯\N{\rE}That's everything. Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.85,1:00:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,5)\an9\fs12\i1}♪我以为会持续一生的爱...\N{\rL}{\i1\fs9}♪ A love I thought would last for a lifetime... ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.52,1:00:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 太可怕了\N{\rE}God, that's awful.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.89,1:00:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那是...\N{\rE}No. That's a...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.23,1:00:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一拳的味道\N{\rE}punch of flavor.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.23,1:00:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是西拉葡萄酒\N{\rE}That's what a Syrah is.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.66,1:00:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你没花太多钱\N{\rE}Hope you haven't spent too much on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.77,1:00:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,要...\N{\rE}To...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.04,1:00:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,敬耶稣基督\N{\rE}To Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.04,1:00:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,生日快乐\N{\rE}Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.25,1:00:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rE}Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.82,1:00:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你一个人住在这里吗\N{\rE}Do you live here alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.22,1:00:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rE}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.12,1:00:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 当然\N{\rE}Oh, uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.49,1:00:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我...不 我不能有室友\N{\rE}I, uh... No, I can't have roommates.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.52,1:00:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢自己的空间\N{\rE}I, um, I like my own space.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.86,1:00:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是喜欢找乐子\N{\rE}I still like to have fun,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.19,1:00:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 我还能发出很大的声音\N{\rE}and, uh, I can make a lot of noise.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.36,1:00:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 你也看到了 我会把事情搞得一团糟\N{\rE}And, uh, I can make a mess, as you can see,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.73,1:00:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我想放多大声就放多大声\N{\rE}but, uh, I can play music as loud as I want to.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.63,1:00:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以...\N{\rE}I can...
