Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.79,1:05:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的 对吧？\N{\rE}You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.82,1:05:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好像这就是文明的堕落\N{\rE}As if that's the downfall of civilization,
