Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.43,1:05:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是男人\N{\rE}especially men.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.74,1:05:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳...\N{\rE}Eileen...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.18,1:05:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在可能已经知道了\N{\rE}as you can probably tell by now,
