Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.78,1:08:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 对不起 求你了 艾琳\N{\rE}I do. I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry. Please, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.58,1:08:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 艾琳给我点时间\N{\rE}Just pl-please, Eileen. Just give me a moment.
