Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.86,1:09:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但不知怎的 我们从楼梯上摔到了地下室\N{\rE}but somehow we fell down the stairs to the basement.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.40,1:09:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为她会杀了我\N{\rE}I-I thought she was gonna kill me,
