Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.25,1:18:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那么对我们大家都好\N{\rE}then it would be better for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.86,1:18:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,的确如此\N{\rE}And it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.13,1:18:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我在做什么 这不是...\N{\rE}I knew what I was doing, it wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.00,1:18:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这不太对\N{\rE}it wasn't quite right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.40,1:18:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我知道\N{\rE}I did know that. I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.90,1:18:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但你会告诉谁呢？你知道吗\N{\rE}But who do you tell? You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.67,1:18:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我能告诉谁呢？\N{\rE}Who could I tell?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.08,1:18:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 你要尽力而为\N{\rE}I mean, you do the best you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.55,1:19:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道有了孩子之后会发生什么吗\N{\rE}You know what happens when you have children?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.76,1:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫看你的眼神从未变过\N{\rE}Your husband never looks at you the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.86,1:19:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但在他和李上床之后\N{\rE}But after he went to bed with Lee,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.60,1:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他会来找我\N{\rE}he'd come to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.47,1:19:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就像卸下了一个沉重的包袱\N{\rE}It was like a big burden had been lifted.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.31,1:19:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他 他很放松\N{\rE}He was, he was relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.31,1:19:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他抱着我的感觉真好\N{\rE}It felt good, how he'd hold me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.82,1:19:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他那时爱我\N{\rE}He loved me then.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.79,1:19:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他会轻声地吻我\N{\rE}He would whisper and kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.56,1:19:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是以前的样子...\N{\rE}It was the way it had been before...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.53,1:19:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那时我们年轻、快乐、相爱\N{\rE}when we were young and happy and in love.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.63,1:19:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉很好\N{\rE}It felt good.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.10,1:19:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这有什么不对吗...\N{\rE}Is that so wrong...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.14,1:19:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,想有这种感觉？\N{\rE}to want to feel like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.65,1:20:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会明白的\N{\rE}You wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.55,1:20:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你还年轻 还没有心碎过\N{\rE}You're young, you haven't had your heart broken.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.83,1:20:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我在流血我在流血\N{\rE}I'm bleeding! I'm bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.20,1:20:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我救救我\N{\rE}Help me! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.93,1:20:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了求...帮帮我\N{\rE}Please! Plea... Help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.57,1:20:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我在流血  - 嘘\N{\rE}- I'm bleeding! - Shh! Shh!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.50,1:20:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 帮帮我你会后悔的  - 艾琳 救救我\N{\rE}- Help me! You'll be sorry! - Eileen, help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.20,1:20:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉所有人你做了什么！\N{\rE}I'll tell everyone what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.71,1:20:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 艾琳  - 医生\N{\rE}- Eileen! - A doctor!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.71,1:20:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,去看医生\N{\rE}Get a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.18,1:20:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 救我出去  - 艾琳 帮帮我\N{\rE}- Get me out of here! - Eileen, help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.28,1:20:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮我\N{\rE}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.02,1:20:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！\N{\rE}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.19,1:20:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rE}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.39,1:20:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！\N{\rE}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.16,1:20:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！\N{\rE}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.83,1:20:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 好的 - 好的\N{\rE}Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.19,1:21:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么向她开枪？\N{\rE}Why did you shoot her?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.86,1:21:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我很难过\N{\rE}I was upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.00,1:22:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在该怎么办？\N{\rE}What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.98,1:22:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们带她去我家\N{\rE}We take her to my house.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.95,1:22:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸总是把枪拿出来\N{\rE}My dad's always whipping his gun out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.29,1:22:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,人人皆知\N{\rE}Everyone knows it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.99,1:22:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以伪装成他是在停电时射杀她的\N{\rE}We can make it look like he shot her in a blackout.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.56,1:22:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是个酒鬼 对吧？\N{\rE}He's just a drunk piece of shit, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.27,1:22:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何他都会死 或者发疯\N{\rE}He's gonna die anyway or go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.01,1:22:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,医生是这么说的\N{\rE}The doctor said so.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.91,1:22:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们带她一起走吧\N{\rE}So let's take her together and leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.01,1:22:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们就可以去纽约过年了...\N{\rE}Then we could go to New York for the New Year...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.91,1:22:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我们两个人\N{\rE}just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.35,1:22:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\rE}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.86,1:22:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\rE}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.93,1:23:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\rE}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.40,1:23:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rE}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.64,1:23:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你先去你父亲家\N{\rE}You go ahead to your father's house.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.18,1:23:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在那儿等我\N{\rE}Wait for me there.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.38,1:23:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我去里面打扫一下\N{\rE}- Yeah. - I'll clean up inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.68,1:23:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能留下任何证据\N{\rE}We can't leave any evidence behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.92,1:23:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我会等你的  - 我会很快的\N{\rE}- I'll be waiting. - I'll be quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.79,1:27:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳\N{\rE}Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.62,1:27:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳\N{\rE}Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.13,1:27:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,继续睡吧 爸爸\N{\rE}Go back to sleep, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.13,1:27:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿？\N{\rE}Where you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.93,1:28:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能要上路了\N{\rE}I might just get on the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.57,1:28:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧\N{\rE}All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.65,1:28:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\rE}Good night.


